message: Reverting violations of neutrality principle - the tone of recent additions to the article are made is derogatory and includes decisively biased and antagonistic commentary. Reverting content that unquestionably violates the non-free content policy (NFCC)
/* Controversy */ Conjecture and speculation, baseless and unsubstantiated claims.

Thanks to the username Samreeveparl, after a quick google of "Sam Reeve Parliament" and then "Sam Reeve ACT Legislative Assembly", I was quick to find that a "Sam Reeve" works at the Legislative Assembly. Hmmm could the Sam Reeve editing the page be the Sam Reeve removing media information about his MLA?!? All information has been linked to multiple media sources and is true and accurate. Any removal is antithetical to an accurate history record of this MLA.
